OL,5, The case against a man facing          
OL,6, historical sexual abuse allegations was
OL,7, stopped after a 30-year-old letter was 
OL,8, uncovered in which prosecutors gave up 
OL,9, their right to prosecute him.          
OL,11,FThe former teacher was facing          
OL,12,Fallegations about his conduct towards a
OL,13,Fpupil in the late 1970s in Ayrshire.   
OL,15,FIt is understood the allegations were  
OL,16,Ffirst made in the 1990s and then       
OL,17,Frevisited by Police Scotland in 2016.  
OL,19,FThe case came to court earlier this    
OL,20,Fmonth but was deserted.                
